Class Circle

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.middleware.rdf.Resource

                • org.universAAL.ontology.shape.Circle

  • public class Circle
extends Ellipse
    Ontological representation of a circle shape. Methods included in this class are the mandatory ones for representing an ontological concept in Java classes for universAAL. Usually it includes getters and setters for most of its properties.
    Author:
    chwirth
